text: Eunidia breuningiae is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Villiers in 1951. It is known from Egypt, Senegal, Niger, Oman, Yemen, Djibouti, Saudi Arabia, and Chad.BioLib.cz - Eunidia breuningiae.
